1. His name is Makar.
2. He is twenty years old.
3. He is a doctor by profession.
4. His eyes are blue.
5. His hair is dark.
6. His favourite sport is baseball.
7. His hobby is sport.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. The Internet is very usefull part of modern life - The Internet isn't very usefull part of modern life.
2. Here is you check - Here's not you check - Here isn't you check.
3. No, thank you, it is too expensive for me - Yes, thank you, it's not too expensive for me - Yes, thank you, it isn't too expensive for me.
4. We are both green-eyed - We're not bot green-eyed - We aren't green-eyed.
5. They are not late - They are late - They're not late - They aren't late.
6. Here are flowers for you! Oh, it is pleasant! - Here're not (aren't) flowers for you! Oh, it's not pleasant.
7. You are cold (ты простудишься). Put on the coat. - You're not (aren't) cold.
8. The sky is not dark today - The sky is dark today - The sky isn't dark today.
9. It is not half past seven - It's not half past seven - It isn't half past seven - It's half past seven.

